<P>
Right-hander Pat Bennett threw a five-hitter and was two for three with three 
runs batted in to lead Encino-Crespi to a 10-2 win over North Hollywood in an 
inter-divisional American Legion District 20 game at Valley College on Tuesday. 
</P>
