Quotron Systems, Los Angeles, has named Anthony P. Hatch vice 
president-corporate communications. Before joining Quotron, Hatch was director 
of corporate public affairs at Times Mirror Co. Quotron Systems delivers 
real-time market data from 67 exchanges. 
