STATES; ROSTENKOWSKI, DAN; TOBACCO; EXCISE TAX -- UNITED STATES; UNITED STATES 
-- BUDGET; FEDERAL DEFICIT; BUSINESS TAX; EMPLOYEE STOCK OWNERSHIP PLANS 
</P>
